      "body" : "I agree that it's so incomprehensible (and not desirable) in its behavior that it's unlikely anyone was using it (or at least, using it _and_ not silently getting screwed over by it).  I do wish any of these queries that only worked  with txindex had a non-txindex mechanism that took a location parameter (e.g. block height.)",
